yden

файл на civitaiстраница на civitai

2023/4/20 更新了 yden-V3

由于V3版本和前两个版本的融合配方完全不同，因此对构图的改变是很大的，但相比前两个版本，V3版本对于手部有良好的表现，尤其是在高steps的条件下。

所有示例图像均使用txt2img功能生成，所使用的VAE为原生VAE。

Due to my poor English proficiency, I used ChatGPT to translate Chinese into English. Please bear with me.

The following is the translated description:

Due to the completely different fusion formula between V3 version and the previous two versions, there are significant changes in composition. However, compared to the previous two versions, V3 version has good performance for hands, especially under high steps conditions.

All example images were generated using txt2img function and native VAE was used.

————————————————————————————————

2023/3/25 更新了 yden-V2

作为yden的新版本，它和V1一样都是为了生成动漫风格的图片而被创造的模型，且同样已被压缩至fp16，它可以在保持原来的效果和速度的同时减少模型大小。

相较于V1版本，V2版本生成的图片画面会更加精细，且构图有比较大的改变。

在参数设置方面和V1版本没有任何区别，另外在此强烈推荐使用Hires.fix功能，以便更好的发挥这个模型的潜力。

————————————————————————————————

以下是yden-V1的介绍

这是一个用来生成动漫风格的模型，我已将该模型压缩成fp16，它可以在保持原来的效果和速度的同时减少模型大小。

示例图像均由novelai原版VAE生成。

以下是推荐参数：

Sampler：DPM++ 2M Karras

steps：22

CFG Scale：7

Negative prompt：(worst quality, low quality:1.4)

Hires.fix：R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6B

Hires steps：10

Denoising strength：0.35-0.6

Upscale by：1.5-2

The caulkinumV1_S series is a model devised to depict realistic and beautiful people and landscapes.

The primary goal of the "S8" series is to depict beautiful people.

I will be very happy if someone likes these models.

caulkinumV2 for Anime Style

файл на civitaiстраница на civitai

※このモデルにはいくつかのバリエーションがあることを見逃さないでください

　Note:Don't miss that there are several variations of this model!

caulkinumV2 series for Anime characters.

Note: If you like it, please give it a STAR MARKS !

,

The caulkinumV2_AR series is a model designed to beautifully portray anime characters and light.

This checkpoint was spawned accidentally through multiple iterations of hierarchical merging.

Therefore, the detailed recipe is already lost.

,

However, there is no doubt that Silicon28 is at the root of it and that it has inherited the influence of ElysiumAnime_V2.

If someone likes it I will be very happy.

,

The caulkinumV2 series has several variations.

"AR" is the first model, which is a modern anime/game style.

  • https://civitai.com/models/32537?modelVersionId=38959

"AR2" is the normal evolution of the first model, and it can create better illustrations.

  • https://civitai.com/models/32537?modelVersionId=48531

"A4FS" has a dramatic style, which is more in line with recent RPG games.

  • https://civitai.com/models/32537?modelVersionId=48630

"ARCT" is an anime-style painting that makes the characters look young.

  • https://civitai.com/models/32537?modelVersionId=48791

"ARc" has the same anime style, but is a bit more difficult to handle and a bit outlandish.

  • https://civitai.com/models/32537?modelVersionId=48898

"NCA" is a little bit special and unique, but it was created to depict a slime girl.

  • https://civitai.com/models/32537?modelVersionId=50350

,

It does not always work, but I am generally satisfied with the results.

CityEdge_ToonMix

файл на civitaiстраница на civitai

This model is for producing toon-like anime images, but it is not based on toon/anime models. This model is based on the photorealistic chilled-regeneric v2 model, and then transformed to toon-like one.

If you use my model "CityEdgeMix", you may notice that same prompt/seed as CityEdgeMix also produces very similar images as CityEdge_ToonMix. CityEdge_ToonMix is based on CityEdgeMix, which is based on chilled-regereric v2, merged some anime/toon models with low coefficients to expand desctiption variations, and then transoformed to a toon-like model.

Both SFW and NSFW is capable. VAE is not needed but you can try some.

アニメ調の出力を得るためのモデルですが、アニメ系のモデルからではなく実写系のモデル（chilled-regereric v2）から出発し、最後にアニメ調のタッチに変換して作成したモデルです。

公開している実写系（chilled-regereric v2ベース）のモデル「CityEdgeMix」に、アニメ系の出力のバリエーションを持たせるためにいくつかのアニメ系モデルを軽くマージし、その後アニメ系の出力モデルに変換しています。ですので、CityEdgeMixと同じプロンプトやシード値を使うと、よく似た出力を得ることができるはずです。

エロ・非エロどちらでも可。VAEは焼き込み済ですが彩度は浅めなので別のものも試してみていいと思います。

Clam

файл на civitaiстраница на civitai

"Clam" is named from using modes' name.

It has better performance in txt2img when using positive prompts to describe what you want without any quality tags, and you can use EasyNegative as negative prompt.

Ver.1.1 has more details. Compared to Ver.1.0, it is too similar to be a Ver.2.0.
